card_text: You can target 1 Normal Monster or 1 "Magikey" monster in your GY; add it to your hand, then you can apply 1 of these effects.$N●Fusion Summon 1 "Magikey" Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck in Defense Position, using monsters from your hand or field as Fusion Material.$N●Ritual Summon 1 "Magikey" Ritual Monster from your hand in Defense Position, by Tributing monsters from your hand or field whose total Levels equal or exceed its Level.
